{"en_US_ConsumerCopy"=>"Our waterproof footwear incorporates a variety of advanced waterproofing materials, treatments and processes. {"en_US_ConsumerCopy"=>"Our \"Does It Fit?\" system for kids' footwear uses a removable footbed to show when a child has outgrown their shoes. {"en_US_ConsumerCopy"=>"Our waterproof footwear incorporates a variety of advanced waterproofing materials, treatments and processes. {"en_US_ConsumerCopy"=>"Our \"Does It Fit?\" system for kids' footwear uses a removable footbed to show when a child has outgrown their shoes.
